00:16.000 --> 00:18.000
No, he's not taken.

00:18.000 --> 00:19.000
Oh, thank you.

00:19.000 --> 00:21.000
Oh, let me help you with this.

00:21.000 --> 00:22.000
Oh, thank you.

00:27.000 --> 00:28.000
